OL,7,FBangladesh's ousted prime minister,
OL,8,FSheikh Hasina, has been sentenced to
OL,9,Fdeath after being found guilty of
OL,10,Fcrimes against humanity.
OL,12,FHer sentence follows the violent
OL,13,Fsuppression of student protests, which
OL,14,Fultimately toppled her government and
OL,15,Fforced her to flee to India last
OL,16,FAugust, ending her 15-year reign.
