OL,7,FProsecutors sought the death penalty
OL,8,Fafter the court heard that about 1,400
OL,9,Fprotesters were killed and up to
OL,10,F25,000 were injured during weeks of
OL,11,Funrest in 2024.
OL,13,FA three-judge panel of the
OL,14,FInternational Crimes Tribunal,
OL,15,FBangladesh's domestic war crimes
OL,16,Fcourt, delivered the verdict on Monday.
