OL,7,FThe tribunal also sentenced former
OL,8,FHome Minister Asaduzzaman Khan to
OL,9,Fdeath, while a retired police chief
OL,10,Freceived a five-year sentence after he
OL,11,Fbecame a state witness against Hasina
OL,12,Fand pleaded guilty.
OL,14,FHasina faced five charges, mainly
OL,15,Faccusing her of inciting the murder of
OL,16,Fprotesters and ordering them to be
OL,17,Fhanged, as well as authorising the use
OL,18,Fof lethal weapons, drones and
OL,19,Fhelicopters to suppress the unrest.
OL,21,FShe denies all charges.
