OL,7,FHer lawyers have criticised the trial
OL,8,Fand last week appealed to the United
OL,9,FNations Special Rapporteur on
OL,10,Fextrajudicial, summary or arbitrary
OL,11,Fexecutions, citing "serious concerns"
OL,12,Fover due process and fair trial rights.
OL,14,FHasina ruled Bangladesh with an iron
OL,15,Ffist from 2009 until she was ousted in
OL,16,F2024.
OL,18,FMonday's sentencing has raised fears
OL,19,Fof fresh political turmoil ahead of
OL,20,Fnational elections expected in
OL,21,FFebruary.
